lead_paragraph: Champions Bayern Munich eased past Hertha Berlin 3-0 on Wednesday to open up a two-point lead at the top of the Bundesliga and inflict the first defeat for their opponents after three straight wins this season.

headline.print_headline: Bayern Carve Out Two-Point Lead at Top With Hertha Win
